    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A – F: Mylonchulus mulveyi Jairajpuri, 1970. A: Anterior region. B: Anterior end. C: female genital tract. D: Vulval region. E: Female posterior end. F: Female tail tip. G – I: Mylonchulus paraindex Ahmad, Baniyamuddin & Jairajpuri, 2005. G: Anterior region. H: Female genital tract. I: Female posterior end (scale bars A – C, G, H = 20 µm, D, E, I = 10 µm; F = 5 µm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/217286/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

